properties.name: target
properties.description:
Specifies the target of the link.

  • If null, the link opens in the same tab.
  • If '_blank', the link opens in a new tab.
properties.rawdescription:
Specifies the target of the link.
- If null, the link opens in the same tab.
- If '_blank', the link opens in a new tab.

properties.description: Doc is shown under Help & Support. Quicklink is displayed bigger and shown at the top.
